            <li>Protect the personal safety of Users of the Service or the public</li>
            <li>Protect against legal liability</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>Your Privacy Rights</h2>
          <p>
            Depending on Your jurisdiction, You may have specific rights regarding Our collection and use of Your Personal Data. We are committed to honoring these rights.
          </p>

          <h3>General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) Privacy</h3>
          <p>
            If You are a resident of the European Economic Area (EEA), the United Kingdom (UK), or Switzerland, You have certain data protection rights, and We aim to take reasonable steps to allow You to correct, amend, delete, or limit the use of Your Personal Data.
          </p>
          <p>
