          </p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>The Right to Access</strong> - The right to request copies of Your Personal Data We hold.</li>
            <li><strong>The Right to Rectification</strong> - The right to request that We correct any information You believe is inaccurate or complete information You believe is incomplete.</li>
            <li><strong>The Right to Erasure</strong> (Right to be Forgotten) - The right to request that We erase Your Personal Data, under certain conditions.</li>
