          </ul>

          <h3>Right to Delete</h3>
          <p>
            You have the right to request the deletion of Your Personal Information that We collected from You, subject to certain exceptions. (This is generally covered by your existing "Delete Your Personal Data" section.)
          </p>

          <h3>Right to Correct</h3>
          <p>
            You have the right to request the correction of inaccurate Personal Information that We maintain about You.
          </p>

          <h3>Right to Opt-Out of Sale or Sharing</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>The Company does not sell Personal Data for monetary consideration</strong> as the term "sell" is traditionally understood.</li>
            <li><strong>However, We may share Personal Data with Service Providers</strong> to provide cross-context behavioral advertising, which may be considered "sharing" or a "sale" under California law.</li>
            <li>You have the right to direct Us to stop "selling" or "sharing" Your Personal Information at any time (the "Right to Opt-Out").</li>
